Heavy vehicles entering Queensland must hold and display a Queensland border pass. For more information: https://www.qld.gov.au/border-pass-confirmation.

properties.headline: CHANGED TRAFFIC CONDITIONS M8 is now open - ST PETERS INTERCHANGE M8 westbound tunnel at Gardeners Rd and Euston Rd/Campbell Rd
properties.otherAdvice:
New traffic conditions are in place on Gardeners Rd and Campbell Rd/Euston Rd at the St Peters Interchange where westbound motorists can enter the new M8 tunnel.

Motorists should check signs on approach to the tunnel, and at the exit at Beverly Hills, to ensure they remain in the correct lane for their destination.

Dangerous goods/prohibited vehicles must not use the M8 and M5 East tunnels. Alternative routes are eastbound via King Georges Rd or Bexley Rd and westbound via Foreshore Rd.

Real-time travel and trip planning information may not be available until sufficient traffic volume data is collected.

For more information on the project visit westconnexm8.com.au.

properties.otherAdvice:
The NSW state government has imposed restrictions on movements to/from Victoria as a result of the coronavirus pandemic.

This border crossing is currently closed - permit holders should use an alternative route to travel between Victoria and NSW.

Transport for NSW is continuing to work closely with NSW Health, NSW Police and industry on a number of important issues including freight operations and logistics.

Visit health.nsw.gov.au for more details.

properties.headline: CHANGED TRAFFIC CONDITIONS - BRINGELLY The Northern Road between Belmore Road AND Thames Road
properties.adviceB: Exercise caution; Allow extra travel time
properties.otherAdvice:
Transport for NSW has built a new interchange at Bringelly, to the east of the existing intersection with Bringelly Road/Greendale Road and The Northern Road.

The new interchange, as well as the newly constructed sections of The Northern Road between Belmore Road and Thames Road, Bringelly will open to final configuration during the day on Thursday 16 July 2020.  

Changes include:

Traffic switch of The Northern Road to newly constructed underpass between Belmore Road and Thames Road. Traffic will be split with one lane travelling north and one travelling south.

Changed access to the existing section of The Northern Road - The old Northern Road will be renamed to Wentworth Road. 

New traffic signals at Bringelly Road interchange will be commissioned on Thursday 16th July.
